videos.description: Arizona State guard Luguentz Dort drains the 3-pointer from the top of the key and is fouled.
videos.headline: ASU freshman Dort hits 3 and is fouled

videos.description: Vanderbilt big man Yanni Wetzell gets the pass and throws down the huge dunk while being fouled.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Wetzell throws down dunk off sweet pass

videos.description: After Arizona State cut into Vanderbilt's lead, Joe Toye nails a 3-pointer from the top of the key to extend the Commodores' lead to 8.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Toye knocks down huge 3
